Sakataren hukumar, Sutopo Purvo Nguroho, ya bayyana a wani taron manema labarai cewa an samu rahotanni da dama na mutane da ke cikin kwari sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da kuma wata guguwa mai tsawon kafa 20 da ta afku a ranar Juma'a.
