Rangers sun kare harbi biyu a raga a farkon rabin, amma tsohon mai tsaron raga na Ibro Liam Kelly ya fuskanci matsaloli daga lasana kolibali da twee ova azaria.
Ko da yake a minti na 34 Livy zai iya yin nasara a wasan, babu wanda zai iya musanta cewa shi kaɗai ne ya cancanci wannan kyautar.
Duk da haka, 'yan wasan Rangers sun kasa tsallake Jacob.
Sa'ad da Deccan Gallagher ya kai ƙwallo ga Scott Robinson, Scott Orfield bai nuna sha'awarsa ba, Scott Robinson ya yi shiru don ya zaɓi Menga don kawai ya gama.
