Amma, Livingstone ya nuna wa baƙi irin wasan da za su iya morewa, ya yi amfani da Lithgo da Hulket don yin wasa da dogon ƙwallo.
Holt ya iya karawa da kansa a mataki na karshe, amma McGregor ya dakatar da Jacobs daga yin nazari sosai kafin Lithgow ya fadi daga kusurwa.
Rangers sun kira Glenn Middleton a matsayin mai maye gurbin, sun sake yin wani jinkiri don fansa saboda sun yi rikici da Jacobs, amma Thompson bai bar su su sake yin nasara ba.
Elmanak: Wanda ya ƙirƙira ma'aunin geyser
Yanzu shafi na kalandarmu ta "Ranar Lahadi": Shekaru 136 da suka shige, ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882 da kuma bayan... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na nan gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiser a Jamus.
Ga hanyar ganowa da auna radiyo, Geiser ya kirkiro na'urar da daga baya aka sani da Geiser counter.
Geyser counter yana daya daga cikin manyan abubuwan da suka shafi kimiyya, ya zama babban abu a al'adun pop, kuma, a cikin 1950, an yi fim din "Bells of Coronado" a kan shi, wanda ya fara nuna masanin kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Me ya sa yake yi wa duniya?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne na'urar da ake amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu guba kamar uranium.
Idan ka kunna waɗannan na'urorin, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ɗin da ke cikin ma'adanai ke yi".
Evans: "Ka gaya mini, yanzu wannan yana fitowa!"
"Hans" Geiser ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, yana da shekara 63.
