Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta yi tambaya game da lalata maza
Kit Harington ya fi saninsa da rawar da ya taka a matsayin John Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai suna Game of Thrones.
Amma, ɗan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi tambaya game da rawar Macho Hero, yana cewa yawanci matasa suna yin wahayi zuwa gare su ta wurin kallon irin waɗannan halayen a kan allo kuma suna jin cewa dole ne su yi aiki mai wuya don samun girmamawa.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta bayyana cewa tana jin 'wani abu ba daidai ba' kuma ta tambayi yadda za a kawar da matsalar cutar da ke haifar da jima'i a zamanin #MeToo.
Kwanan nan, Kit ta auri Rose Leslie, mai shekara 31, wadda ta yi aiki tare da ita a wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, kuma ta ce tana da 'taƙama' wajen tattauna batun.
Ya ce, "Ni kaina ina da tabbacin cewa a yanzu - shin muna yin wani abu ba daidai ba game da jima'i?
"Shin muna koya wa maza cewa idan sun girma kamar yadda muke yi, za su fuskanci matsalolin da ke kan allo?"
Kit ya yi tunanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na abin da ke haddasa lalataccen jima'i, ya gode wa yawan maza da ke cikinta.
Ya ci gaba: 'Mene ne ake yi kuma menene ake koyarwa?
Abin da ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi, yana sa matasa maza su gaskata cewa dole ne su yi wasu abubuwa domin su zama maza?
Ina ganin wannan ya zama babbar tambaya ta zamaninmu, ta yaya za mu kawo canji?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba game da tunanin samari. '
A cikin wata hira da aka yi da shi, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai shiga cikin wani shiri na gaba ko na gaba ba lokacin da Game of Thrones ya sake dawowa a ƙarshen bazara, kuma ya ce ya yi 'waje-waje da kuma tafiye-tafiye da yawa.'
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi aiki a sabon shirin True West na Sam Shepard, wanda ke game da wani mai shirya fim wanda ɗan'uwansa ɗan fashi ne.
Kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa abu mafi kyau da ya faru da shi daga Game of Thrones shi ne ya sadu da matarsa Rose.
Ta ce, "Na samu abokiyar aurena ta wannan shirin, don haka na yi imani cewa wannan shirin ya ba ni iyalina na nan gaba kuma rayuwata ta ci gaba daga nan".
Rose ta taka rawar Yugrit, wacce ke da abokin aikin Kit, John Snow, a cikin kyautar Emmy Award.
A watan Yunin 2018, ma'auratan sun yi aure a Leslie, Scotland, tare da yardar dangi.
HIV/AIDS: Rahoton ya nuna cewa, sabon kamuwa da cutar ya karu da kashi 14 cikin 100 a kasar Sin.
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane sama da 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a duk fadin kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kawai, an sami kusan sabbin shari'o'i 40,000.
