Taron Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekara ta 2012, wani ci gaba ne na kungiyar tallafawa kasa da kasa, Global Poverty Project, wadda ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki da talauci.
