Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba da ta gabata game da biyan kudin jaridar China Daily a cikin babban jaridar Iowa mai suna Des Moines Register, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
