Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da ya buga wasan Ryder Cup na 47, amma dole ne ya canza fasalinsa don kauce wa wannan mummunan abin mamaki.
A karo na 12 da yake buga wasan a shekara biyu, Mickelson ya yi wasa a ranar Asabar da kyaftin Jim Furyk ya yi wa Foursom wasa.
Maimakon zama abin jan hankali, kamar yadda ya kasance sau da yawa ga Amurka, babban mai nasara sau biyar ya ciyar da kwanakinsa yana zaune a cikin masu farin ciki kuma yana aiki a cikin bege na gyara raunin da ya yi wasa.
Ba ya taɓa yin tuki a kai tsaye a lokacin da ya tsufa, amma ɗan shekara 48 bai dace da filin wasan Tite Le Golf National ba, inda ake yawan hukunta waɗanda suka yi jinkiri don yin kuskuren harbi.
Kuma a lokacin da hanya ba ta da sauƙi, a wasan tara na ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai yi yaƙi da Francisco Molinari, wanda ya ci nasara a gasar British Open, wanda ya yi wasa tare da rookie Tommy Fleetwood don lashe duk wasanninsa huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amurka, waɗanda suka fara wasa da maki huɗu a ƙasa a wasanni 12 na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa, suka fara wasa da ƙarfi, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya amince da mutumin, ba wai zai iya cewa wani abu ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayinsa sosai, ya yi mini ta'aziyya, ya rungume ni, ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe.
"Yana da tabbaci sosai.
Shi ɗan zauren zauren wasan kwaikwayo ne kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga waɗannan ƙungiyoyin a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin cewa zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin cewa zan yi fiye da haka, amma ya yi daidai da yadda muka yi tsammani za mu ci gaba.
Yana son fita waje kamar kowa".
Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a ranar Lahadi don wasan da aka fi buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan zai iya nuna ƙarshen Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa taɓa taɓa ƙimar rikodin kansa ba.
Mickelson ya ci nasara 18, ya yi hasara 20, kuma ya yi wasan rabin lokaci bakwai, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa yana kawo wasu kusanci a cikin tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da amsa, yana son yin ba'a, kuma kasancewarsa a cikin ɗakin tawagar abu ne na musamman", in ji shi.
"Ina ganin matasa 'yan wasa ma sun ji daɗin ziyararsu a wannan makon, wanda abin farin ciki ne a gani.
Ya ba da fiye da wasa kawai".
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin na Turai ya san cewa babban gefe zai iya ɓacewa nan ba da daɗewa ba.
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin na Turai, ya san cewa samun babban ci gaba a wasan Ryder Cup a ranar ƙarshe na wasan zai iya zama da sauƙi.
Dan ya fara wasa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama, inda wani ɓangare na ƙungiyar da ke ƙarƙashin jagorancin Seve Ballesteros ya ci gaba da ci gaba da biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma tare da nasara 141⁄2-131⁄2, tare da mafi ƙarancin gefe, kawai ya isa layin ƙarshe.
"Kuna tuna wa kanku cewa muna da babban ci gaba a Valderama; muna da babban ci gaba a Brooklyn, inda muka yi asara, kuma a Valderama, mun yi nasara kawai", bayan kallon ajin 2018 sun yi nasara da 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da kuma 10-6 a Le Golf National a jiya, Burnior ya ce, yana tunani.
Saboda haka tarihi zai nuna mini da kuma dukan waɗanda suke cikin wannan tawagar cewa ba a gama ba.
Za ku biya duk kuɗin gobe.
Ku fita can ku yi duk abin da ya dace.
Ba a gama ba sai ka sami maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa guda, ita ce mu ci wannan kofin kuma a nan ne za mu ci gaba da mai da hankali.
Na ko da yaushe ina cewa, ina mai da hankali ne a kan 'yan wasa 12 da suke gefenmu, amma mun san cewa manyan 'yan wasa a duniya suna gefenmu".
Bjorn ya ci gaba da cewa game da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi nasara a kan hanya mai wuya: "Ba zan taɓa yin nasara a kan kaina ba.
Gobe lokaci ne mai wuya.
Za a gabatar da wani mutum-mutumin a gobe, kuma wannan abu ne na daban.
Yana da kyau ka je wurin da abokin ka yake sa'ad da abubuwa suke tafiya daidai, amma idan ka je wurin kai da kanka, za ka iya gwada iyawarka a matsayin ɗan wasan golf.
Wannan shi ne saƙon da kuke bukata ku isar wa 'yan wasanku cewa su yi iya ƙoƙarinsu gobe.
Yanzu, ka bar abokin aikinka ya tafi, kuma dole ne ya yi iyakar ƙoƙarinsa".
Jim Furyk, wanda ya yi tsayayya da Bjorn, ya yi fatan cewa 'yan wasansa za su yi fice a matsayin abokan wasa, ban da Jordan Speith da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ci uku cikin huɗu.
Kafin Turai ta yi masa "mu'ujiza a Madina", Furyck da kansa ya kasance a ƙarshen waɗannan manyan juyin juya halin kwanaki na ƙarshe, a matsayin ɓangare na ƙungiyar nasara a Brooklyn.
"Na tuna da kowane kalma", in ji shi, lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda kyaftin Ben Cranshaw ya bi da 'yan wasansa a ranar ƙarshe a shekara ta 1999.
Muna da wasanni 12 masu muhimmanci a gobe, amma za ku so ku fara da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brooklyn, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madina.
Idan wannan motsi na tafiya ne a hanya guda, zai sa matches a tsakanin su su yi wahala sosai.
Mun tsara jerinmu kuma mun haɗa mutane a hanyar da muka ji, kun san, muna ƙoƙarin yin wasu abubuwan al'ajabi gobe. "
An ba Thomas aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar kai hari tare da Rory McClaroy a wasan saman, inda Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter su ne manyan rabin sauran jerin Turai.
"Na tsara su cikin wannan tsari domin ina ganin ya rufe su duka", in ji Bjorn game da zaɓinsa na ɗaya.
An sake dakatar da sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
Sabbin jiragen ruwan yakin Jamus da aka tsara don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War-era da aka yi a shekarar 2014, amma saboda tsarin da ba su da kyau da kuma tsada mai saurin tashi, hakan ba zai faru ba har sai a shekara mai zuwa, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
Kamar yadda wata majiya ta soja ta ruwaito daga jaridar Die Zeit, an dage ƙaddamar da Rhineland -Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwan sabon rukunin Baden - Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin rundunar a shekarar 2014, amma batutuwan da ke damun bayan isar da sako sun shafi makomar wannan shiri mai matukar muhimmanci.
An ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa guda huɗu na Baden - Württemberg a cikin 2007 don maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen -class da suka yi tsufa.
An fahimci cewa za su ba da damar yin amfani da manyan bindigogi, makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar ƙananan radar, infrared da acoustic division.
Wasu muhimman halaye sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - yana yiwuwa a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa daga tashar jiragen ruwa na gida har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen yaƙi na zamani - da za su ba wa Jamus damar yin aikin lantarki a ƙasashen waje - za su zama marasa amfani a lokacin da za su shiga hidima, in ji Dai Zein.
Jirgin ruwan F125 mai ban tsoro ya yi ta zubowa a cikin labarai a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin Jamus ta ƙi amincewa da aikin jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa Blohm & Voss Shipyard a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Mutane kalilan ne suka san dalilin janyewar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi nuni da wasu muhimman "rashin ingantattun kayan aiki da na'urori" da suka sa jirgin ya kasa aiki idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Rashin wadatar da aka samu a cikin software ya kasance da muhimmanci domin jiragen Baden - Württemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - rabin ma'aikatan jirgin da ke cikin rukunin jiragen yaƙi na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon da rundunar ta yi na haɓaka haɓaka.
An ce Rhineland - Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka na jiragen ruwa iri ɗaya da aka yi amfani da su a Jamus a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da kayan aikin da ba su da kyau, farashin duk aikin - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - yana zama batun.
An ce ya tashi daga €2.2 biliyan zuwa €3.1 biliyan ($3.6bn).
Matsalar sababbin jiragen ruwa, da suka zama masu muhimmanci musamman a cikin hasken gargaɗi na kwanan nan, suna hana ƙarfin sojojin Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekara, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokoki ta Jamus ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna "ƙarewar jiragen ruwa masu iya turawa".
Jami'in ya ce batun ya zama mai tsanani a tsawon lokaci, yayin da aka cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa daga amfani, amma ba a samar da wasu jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya ce babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwan Baden-Württemberg da suka samu shiga cikin rundunar.
