Indonesia tana zaune a kan Pacific Ring of Fire a fannin girgizar ƙasa kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afka wa ƙasashe 14 a gabar yamma ta lardin Ake na Arewacin Sumatra, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, rabin su a cikin Ake.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yamma na Sumatra a watan Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe ɗarurruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Tsunami mai girma 6.8 ya afka tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ya kashe mutane 700 a gabar tekun kudu.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke gaɓar tekun Sumatra, ta sa tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ruwan sama a AK ta afkawa yankin Pidi Jaya, ta sa mutane su gudu domin ta tunatar da su irin ɓarna da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka yi a shekara ta 2004.
Ba a yi wata annobar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine -gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta yi wa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya ɓarna, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine -gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido marasa taimako na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin saboda cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama shi ne saboda zargin da ya yi wa babban dan Sara Palin, gwamnan Alaska ta gabas kuma mataimakiyar shugaban kasa.
Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi ne saboda zargin tashin hankali na cikin gida, ya yi magudi da rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida, kuma ya yi adawa da kama, a cewar rahoton da jihar Alaska ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
