Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin na NYC
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga Safuolo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa na musamman da aka yi a jihar don aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipow, 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar hanyar da ke yammacin Manhattan a watan Oktoba, yana kashe masu tafiya da keke da masu hawan keke.
A cewar rahoton da aka bayar na neman hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin New York, don a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "tunanin" kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya "tunanin" cutar da su da jiki.
Waɗannan ƙasashe biyu suna ba da hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardun kotu.
Mako guda bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukunci kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da suka hada da huɗu na kisan kai don taimakawa wajen yin fashin baki, wanda ake amfani da shi musamman a shari'o'in aikata laifuka da tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "daidaitaccen shiri da kuma tunani", suna mai bayanin yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi cikin "matsananci, zalunci da mugunta".
"Safulaw Habibulavik Saipov ya ji rauni kuma ya cutar da abokai da iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves Enlar Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Eliz, Hernan Ferrucci, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Elzandro Pagunco", in ji sanarwar da aka bayar.
A cikin waɗanda suka mutu, biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
An yi shari 'ar hukuncin kisa na baya - baya a cikin yankin kudancin New York na tsawon shekaru goma.
An samu mai laifi Khalid Brain da laifin kashe masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekarar 2009.
An yanke musu hukuncin kisa a karo na ƙarshe a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka same su da laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An yanke wa Joan Rosenberg hukuncin kisa ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
