Yadda Yakin Ciniki Tsakanin Amurka Da China Zai Iya Zama Mai Kyau Ga Beijing
Farkon salvo na yaƙin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya kasance mai jinkiri kuma yayin da yaƙin bai ƙare ba tukuna, ɓarna tsakanin ƙasashen na iya zama mai fa'ida ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ce an yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da ake fitarwa na kasar Sin, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi mahimmancin karuwa a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji, wanda ya shafi abubuwa har da dala biliyan 200 (ɗaliban fam 150), wanda ke tasiri fiye da rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta yi ta mayar da martani a kowane lokaci, kwanan nan ta kafa haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma na dala biliyan 60 na kayayyakin Amurka.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin hada Amurka da juna, kuma wataƙila tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu zai yi sanyi nan ba da jimawa ba.
Samun Washington baya yana nufin cewa yin watsi da bukatun, amma a fili ya sunkuyar da kai ga Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Har ila yau, masana sun ce Beijing na iya yin abin da ta ga dama, yaƙin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci, yana rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani saurin yanke shawara a siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayi wanda zai iya fara tallestspin tattalin arziki a cikin ƙasar, wanda ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka gani a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, wani jami'in bincike da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta New America, wani tunani.
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce Syria 'a shirye take' ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar
Kasar Siriya ta ce a shirye take ta mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta yi fama da yakin da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Walid Al-Ma'ulam ya ce, yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci, yanayin a kan ƙasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da sake gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'ada.
Duk yanayi yanzu ya kasance don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira na son rai zuwa kasar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye wanda ke niyya ga rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Sauran mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar har yanzu suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Ma'ulam ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya nanata cewa ba zai yarda da taimakon da aka ba shi ba ko kuma taimakon da aka ba shi daga ƙasashen da suka tallafa wa tawayen.
Turai ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke tawagar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe daga 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu dai Amurka ta sha kashi shida a jere a nahiyar Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun daga 1993.
Lokacin da dan Denmark Thomas Jorn ya kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ya doke Amurkawa, Turai ta sake lashe gasar.
Phil Mickelson, tauraron Amurka, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya nuna T-Shot a cikin ruwa a kan rami na 16th ta hanyar karbar wasa daga Francisco Molinari.
Molinari, ɗan wasan Italiya, shi ne na farko cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka ci 5-0-0 a duk zagayen da suka yi tun lokacin da aka fara tsarin gasar a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Speeth ya ci Denmark ta Thorbjone Olesen da ci 5 da 4 a kan dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a cikin 'yan wasan Turai.
Dustin Donson, wanda shi ne dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya, ya ci Lance Poulter na Ingila da ci 2 da 1, wanda shi ne zai yi wasan Ryder Cup na ƙarshe.
Wani gogaggen ɗan takara na gasar Ryder Cup takwas, Spaniard Sergio Garcia ya zama ɗan Turai wanda ya ci gasar sau ɗaya a duk lokacin da ya ci gasar tare da maki 25.5 na aikin.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma a yau, ba zan iya kame kaina ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Saboda haka na gode wa Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya ba ni gaskiya.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na dawo da kofin.
Wannan game da tawagar ne, kuma ina farin cikin cewa na iya taimakawa", in ji Gracia cikin motsin rai bayan lashe gasar Turai.
Ya ba da haske ga abokin wasan sa John Ram, wanda ya doke Tiger Wood, wani dan wasan golf na Amurka, da ci 2 da 1 a wasan daya da aka yi ranar Lahadi.
Rahim, mai shekara 23, ya ce, "Ina alfahari sosai da na doke Tiger Wood, na girma ina kallon sa".
Wood ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni huɗu da ya yi a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da tarihin Ryder Cup na 13-21-3 a aikinsa.
Ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a tarihi ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 a matsayin na biyu bayan Jack Nichols.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ta gwagwarmaya don neman hanyar da za ta yi nasara a duk karshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finney, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf da dukan ƙarfinsa a dukan gasar.
"Ina alfahari da waɗannan yara, sun yi yaƙi", in ji kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furke bayan wasan da ya yi.
A safiya, muna matsa wa Turai.
Mun ci su.
Barka da zuwa ga Thomas.
Kyaftin ne mai kyau.
Duka 'yan wasan 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Za mu sake tsarawa, zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma zan ci gaba da aiki tare da Thosum.
Ina son waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftinansu.
Ya kamata ka yi musu sallama.
Mun yi wasa da kyau".
Red Tide Update: Ƙarƙashin ƙwayoyin cuta a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahotanni daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida sun nuna cewa akwai raguwar yawan Red Tide a wani ɓangare na yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton yanayin fashewar fashewa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Coolir County - wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali.
Red Tide ya kai kusan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Ana iya samun takunkumi a kusan mil 10 na gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare kaɗan fiye da makon da ya gabata.
Za a iya ganin Red Tide a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an ba da rahoton matsakaiciyar ma'auni a cikin ko a gefen tekun Pinellas County, mafi ƙarancin ma'auni a cikin Hillsborough County, mafi girma daga baya a cikin Manatee County, mafi girma daga baya a cikin Sarasota County, matsakaiciyar ma'auni daga baya a cikin Charlotte County, mafi girma daga baya a cikin yankin na Lee County, da ƙananan ma'auni a cikin Collier County.
An ci gaba da samun rahotanni na cututtukan numfashi a Penellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier Counties.
Babu wani ƙauyen da aka ba da rahoton annobar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
